              | $5.00
            div.input-group
              input.text-center.form-control(type='text' placeholder='1')
              span.input-group-btn
                button.btn.btn-default(type='button') +
                button.btn.btn-default(type='button') -
              span Quantity
            span.input-group-btn
              button#addToCartBtn1.btn.btn-primary
                i.fa.fa-shopping-cart
                | &nbsp;Buy
            .desc
              h3.page-header DESCRIPTION
              p
                | Hundreds of celebrities sat here. Enter for a chance to win this unique couch and show it off to your friends at home. Sit where the celebrities sat!
